  "2388460": {
    "name": "Pathfinder: Gallowspire Survivors",
    "steam_appid": 2388460,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": " <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388460/extras/49a780537f517879f74052e3ba846369.poster.avif?t=1715713819\" width=614 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388460/extras/49a780537f517879f74052e3ba846369.webm?t=1715713819\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388460/extras/49a780537f517879f74052e3ba846369.mp4?t=1715713819\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>《Pathfinder: Gallowspire Survivors》是一款以《Pathfinder》超人氣幻想世界為背景的全新生存類遊戲。在這款遊戲中，你將化身三大英雄之一，帶上一名無畏的夥伴勇闖《Pathfinder》傳說中的黑暗之塔「斷魂塔」(Gallowspire)。你們必須完成不可能的任務，封印即將毀天滅地的黑暗勢力。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要特性</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>从我们的天赋树到我们的敌人，一切都源自受欢迎的Pathfinder IP。<br></li><li>选择战士、盗贼或法师，每个都拥有独特的能力和风格。<br></li><li>参与精心打造的boss战，提升挑战。<br></li><li>深入探索超过67个能力和36个天赋的武器库，实现无尽的策略。<br></li><li>探索16个楼层，跨越3个生态区，与12个小boss和4个史诗级boss战斗。<br></li><li>享受社区请求的功能，如超模式、瞄准&amp;冲刺机制、药水带、详细角色表等。<br></li><li>发现官方Pathfinder艺术收藏品，为英雄提供永久增强。<br></li><li>通过5个难度等级战斗，获得更具挑战性的旅程。<br></li><li>通过Steam远程游戏与朋友组队，一起战斗至胜。<br></li><li>完全兼容Steam Deck，支持在移动中游戏。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388460/extras/511f4869d3e3f88a1fffe64fc9dbcfa5.poster.avif?t=1715713819\" width=614 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388460/extras/511f4869d3e3f88a1fffe64fc9dbcfa5.webm?t=1715713819\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388460/extras/511f4869d3e3f88a1fffe64fc9dbcfa5.mp4?t=1715713819\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >選擇你的夥伴</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388460/extras/3ffe0b7c79b2f4c9870d11c6bf50eaa5.poster.avif?t=1715713819\" width=614 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388460/extras/3ffe0b7c79b2f4c9870d11c6bf50eaa5.webm?t=1715713819\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388460/extras/3ffe0b7c79b2f4c9870d11c6bf50eaa5.mp4?t=1715713819\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>面對黑暗，你並非孤身一人。你可以從其他英雄中選擇一位夥伴，與主要英雄一起出生入死。他們將與你並肩作戰，提供保護與火力支援。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >自訂角色發展</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388460/extras/1cd2b75716fc6abf7a4f3ba3eed0792f.poster.avif?t=1715713819\" width=614 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388460/extras/1cd2b75716fc6abf7a4f3ba3eed0792f.webm?t=1715713819\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388460/extras/1cd2b75716fc6abf7a4f3ba3eed0792f.mp4?t=1715713819\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>吸收敵軍賴以為生的死靈精華並增強自身力量，你可以用塔巴方的黑暗魔法對付他！根據《Pathfinder》RPG 完整的規則系統，你可以透過獨特的天賦、武器和法術發展出獨一無二的角色成長史。<br><br>請慎選角色的能力，因為你需要一座所向披靡的火藥庫，才能闖過斷魂塔的致命考驗。你可以升級武器、法術和被動技能，達到超乎想像的強大破壞力。<br><br>自由分配屬性點至《Pathfinder》標誌性的屬性類別：力量、敏捷、體魄、智力、感知、魅力。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >戰利品尋寶</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388460/extras/8dfea6151558e33894d8317a85fd1bf3.poster.avif?t=1715713819\" width=614 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388460/extras/8dfea6151558e33894d8317a85fd1bf3.webm?t=1715713819\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388460/extras/8dfea6151558e33894d8317a85fd1bf3.mp4?t=1715713819\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在冒險旅途中，你可以探索地下城並開啟隱藏寶箱以蒐集寶物。隨後投擲 20 面骰，讓命運決定你能否一夕致富。<br><br>使用金幣即可永久升級消耗品，例如治療藥水，或能夠暫時賦予強大法術效果的藥水。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >精选于</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388460/extras/dd60ae32b4146b470f6de185eb98bf55.avif?t=1715713819\" width=600 height=104 /></span>",
